WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500
<v Kavya>Alright team, let's kick off the Project Phoenix sync. Gupta, product side se kya updates hain?</v>

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:13.200
<v Gupta>Hi everyone. So, the launch is slightly delayed. We are pushing it to next Wednesday. Security audit clear nahi hua abhi tak.</v>

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:19.800
<v Gupta>Because of this, we need to inform the external marketing agency, Ogilvy, so they pause the ad campaigns.</v>

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.500
<v Gupta>Kavya, can you please email Ogilvy today and let them know about the revised Wednesday launch date?</v>

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
<v Kavya>Haan, I will draft the email to Ogilvy and send it before lunch. No problem.</v>

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:36.000
<v Kavya>Moving to tech updates... Prabal, what is the status of the backend API? Kal load testing fail ho rahi thi.</v>

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:43.500
<v Prabal>Yeah, maine subah logs check kiye. The database queries on the user-profile table are taking too long. Indexing gayab hai usme.</v>

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
<v Prabal>It's a critical fix. Main ek ticket create karta hoon for adding DB indexes and I'll deploy the fix today.</v>

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:54.500
<v Kavya>Okay, please prioritize that. Ashish, frontend pe kya bacha hai? The payment gateway integration is done?</v>

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:59.000
<v Ashish>Mostly done. But Gupta mentioned yesterday that the checkout button copy needs to change from 'Submit' to 'Pay Now'.</v>

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:04.000
<v Gupta>Yes, the design team requested that. Can you push that update to the web-frontend repository?</v>

00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:09.500
<v Ashish>Theek hai. I will log an issue in GitHub for the checkout button text and raise a PR by evening.</v>

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.000
<v Kavya>Awesome. Shubham, QA status? UAT start ho gaya kya?</v>

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:21.000
<v Shubham>Main staging pe testing start kar raha hoon, but Prabal, mujhe admin dashboard ke test credentials chahiye. Mere purane passwords expire ho gaye hain.</v>

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:26.500
<v Prabal>Ah, my bad. Main abhi DB issue debug kar raha hoon. Can you just ping me on Teams after 2 PM? Main generate karke de dunga.</v>

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:31.000
<v Shubham>Done. I'll drop you a message at 2 PM for the admin credentials.</v>

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:38.000
<v Gupta>Guys, ek important cheez miss ho rahi hai. Project Phoenix release notes kaun update kar raha hai on the internal Wiki?</v>

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:44.000
<v Gupta>We need all the v2 feature documentation completed before the launch otherwise support team ko kuch nahi pata hoga.</v>

00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:48.500
<v Kavya>Oh right. The release notes are super important. We definitely need to document the v2 features.</v>

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:53.000
<v Shubham>Haan, otherwise customer success waale humari jaan kha jayenge.</v>

00:01:53.500 --> 00:01:58.000
<v Kavya>Agreed. Let's ensure that gets done. Anything else pending?</v>

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:04.000
<v Ashish>Actually, I need to look into the new Figma mockups for the user dashboard redesign. I'll review them tomorrow.</v>

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:08.000
<v Kavya>Cool. Chalo, let's wrap this up. Thanks everyone!</v>